#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:13
msgid ""
"A background picture in your 3D View is very helpful in many situations: "
"modeling is obviously one, but it is also useful when painting (e.g. you can "
"have reference pictures of faces when painting textures directly on your "
"model...), or animation (when using a video as background), etc."
msgstr ""
"Une image d'arrière-plan dans votre Vue 3D est très utile dans beaucoup de "
"situations : la modélisation en est évidemment une, mais c'est aussi utile "
"pour la peinture (ex. vous pouvez avoir des images de référence de faces "
"lors de l'application directe de texture sur votre modèle...), ou "
"l'animation (utilisation d'une vidéo comme arrière-plan), etc. "

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:21
msgid "Background images are only available for orthographic views."
msgstr ""
"Les images d'arrière-plan ne sont disponibles que dans dans les vues "
"orthographiques."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:25
msgid "Settings"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:31
msgid "Axis"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:31
msgid ""
"Choose which views the image is visible from. This is helpful when you have "
"several reference images from different views (e.g. top, front and side)."
msgstr ""
"Choisissez dans quelles vues l'image est visible. C'est pratique quand vous "
"avez plusieurs images de référence dans différentes vues (ex. top, front and "
"side)."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:38
msgid "Data Source"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:34
msgid "The source of the background image."
msgstr "La source de l'image d'arrière-plan."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:36
msgid "Image"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:37
msgid "Use an external image, image sequence, video file or generated texture."
msgstr ""
"Utilise une image externe, une séquence d'images, un fichier vidéo ou une "
"texture générée. "

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:38
msgid "Movie Clip"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:39
msgid "Use one of the Movie Clip data-blocks."
msgstr "Utilise un des data-blocks du clip vidéo."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:40
msgid "Opacity"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:41
msgid "Controls the transparency of the background image."
msgstr "Contrôle la transparence de l'image d'arrière-plan."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:42
msgid "Front/Back"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:43
msgid ""
"Choose whether the image is shown behind all objects, or in front of "
"everything."
msgstr ""
"Choisissez si l'image sera affichée derrière tous les objets, ou en avant de "
"tout."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:52
msgid "Stretch/Fit/Crop"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:45
msgid "Controls how the image is placed in the camera view."
msgstr "Contrôle la manière dont l'image est placée dans la vue Caméra."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:47
msgid "Stretch"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:48
msgid ""
"Forces the image dimensions to match the camera bounds (may alter the aspect "
"ratio)."
msgstr ""
"Force les dimensions de l'image à correspondre aux limites de la caméra "
"(peut altérer le rapport hauteur/largeur)."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:49
msgid "Fit"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:50
msgid ""
"Scales the image down to fit inside the camera view without altering the "
"aspect ratio."
msgstr ""
"Redimensionne l'image pour l'ajuster dans la vue Caméra sans altérer le "
"rapport hauteur/largeur. "

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:52
msgid "Crop"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:52
msgid ""
"Scales the image up so that it fills the entire camera view, but without "
"altering the aspect ratio (some of the image will be cropped)"
msgstr ""
"Redimensionne l'image de manière qu'elle remplisse la vue caméra, mais sans "
"altérer le format de l'image (certaines parties de l'images seront coupées). "

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:58
msgid "X/Y"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:55
msgid "Position the background image using these offsets."
msgstr "Positionne l'image d'arrière-plan en utilisant ces décalages."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:57
#, python-format
msgid ""
"In orthographic views, this is measured in the normal scene units. In the "
"camera view, this is measured relative to the camera bounds (0.1 will offset "
"it by 10% of the view width/height)"
msgstr ""
"Dans les vues orthographiques, ceci est mesuré en unités de scène normales. "
"Dans le vue Caméra, la mesure est relative aux limites de la caméra (0.1 "
"correspond à un décalage de 10 % de la largeur/hauteur de la vue)"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:60
msgid "Flip Horizontally"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:61
msgid ""
"Swap the image around, such that the left side is now on the right, and the "
"right now on the left."
msgstr ""
"Tourne l'image de sorte que le côté gauche est maintenant à droite, et "
"inversement."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:62
msgid "Flip Vertically"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:63
msgid ""
"Swap the image around, such that the top side is now on the bottom, and the "
"bottom now on the top."
msgstr ""
"Tourne l'image de sorte que le haut est maintenant en bas, et inversement. "

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:64
msgid "Rotation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:65
msgid "Rotate the image around its center."
msgstr "Tourne l'image autour de son axe."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:68
msgid "Size"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/display/background_images.rst:67
msgid "Scale the image up or down from its center."
msgstr "Agrandit ou réduit l'image depuis son centre."
